<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">انظر:</span> <span class="c2">((جامع الأصول)</span>) <span class="c2">(١٠/٢١٣)</span> .<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٥٨٣ -<span class="c5"> حديث:</span> <span class="c2">((كل المسلم على المسلم حرام؛ دمه، وعرضه، وماله)</span>) .<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>- <span class="c2">(٤/٢٢٢٥)</span> .<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
